Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:01.76,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Certifique-se de deixá-los vivos
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:03.83,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Como se nada tivesse acontecido
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:08.98,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Sinta seus lábios prestes a fechar e diga a ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:13.53,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Você não deve se arrepender de nada, apenas tenha esperança
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:18.79,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Isso, para você, seria ser muito gentil
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:23.50,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}E vamos fazer mais vezes... quantas você quiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:29.50,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Mas apenas... não fuja!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:21.85,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}It was something nice and sweet ’til I see the real
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:30.36,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}It’s been always something cruel, dark and sore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.36,0:21:34.99,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}Chikazuku dabi kirameku tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:39.03,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}Konomune oshiyoseru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:43.01,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}Ureshii demo kurushii
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:47.37,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}Koko kara saki wa muri ni chikazukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:52.05,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Yasashii koe de
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.05,0:21:56.33,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Tada kono mama de itai dake
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:22:00.64,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Yusaburanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:03.81,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:12.93,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Daremo kuzusenai kizukiageta barikeedo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:25.96,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Kataku tozashiteta hazu datta no ni doushite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:39.72,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Do you hear weary heart’s S.O.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:21.85,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}Foi algo agradável e doce... até que ganhei juízo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:30.36,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}Sempre foi algo cruel, escuro e doloroso
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.36,0:21:34.99,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}Toda vez que eu me aproximo... toda vez que eu brilho
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:39.03,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}meu peito começa a acelerar
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:43.01,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}Estou feliz, mas dói
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:47.37,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}De agora em diante, eu não deveria me forçar
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:52.05,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Mas diga com uma voz mais suave...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.05,0:21:56.33,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Eu só quero ficar assim
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:22:00.64,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Não me force assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:03.81,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Porém...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:12.93,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Era para ser uma fortaleza que ninguém iria penetrar
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:25.96,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Deveria ser impenetrável, mas por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:39.72,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Você ouve o chamado de emergência deste coração?
